snippet.title: ShootersPool - Billiards Simulation
snippet.description:
New trailer from ShootersPool - Billiards Simulation, released after the 1.8 game update, which suposes the biggest step forward in terms of gameplay & physics improvements and introduces new TOP billiards brands and their products in the game.

What are you waiting to try it? 👉http://bit.ly/2ZJyY3C

Share this video: 
👉 https://youtu.be/Y8e6OLCzYVQ
